      <title>五角大楼负责人前往柬埔寨与中国盟友重建关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/pentagon-chief-heads-to-cambodia-to-renew-ties-with-china-ally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀于周二访问柬埔寨，试图在柬埔寨与中国不断扩大的安全和经济关系导致两国关系紧张的背景下，重建与中国在东南亚最热心盟友的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/pentagon-chief-heads-to-cambodia-to-renew-ties-with-china-ally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:19:43 GMT</pubDate>
