    <item>
      <title>德国部长预计欧洲央行将很快降息，并希望后续行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/german-minister-expects-ecb-rate-cut-soon-hopes-more-follow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国经济部长罗伯特哈贝克表示，他希望欧洲央行本周开始其广受期待的货币宽松周期后，将会进一步降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/german-minister-expects-ecb-rate-cut-soon-hopes-more-follow</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:04:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜向韩国投放装满垃圾的气球后，韩国将停止与朝鲜的边境协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-korea-to-halt-border-deal-with-north-after-it-sends-trash-filled-balloons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜向韩朝边境投放近 1,000 个装满垃圾的气球，以进行所谓的“人类败类”运动。此后，韩国将暂停 2018 年与朝鲜达成的旨在缓解军事紧张局势的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/south-korea-to-halt-border-deal-with-north-after-it-sends-trash-filled-balloons</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:01:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
